## Docker Compose 部署结构
### 新增文件
```
docker/
  docker-compose.yaml              ← 现有（应用节点，小改）
  docker-compose.middleware.yaml   ← 新增（中间件）
  docker-compose.lb.yaml           ← 新增（前置LB）
  nginx/
    nginx.conf                     ← 现有（应用内nginx，不动）
    lb.conf                        ← 新增（前置LB配置）
  middleware/
    init-postgres.sql              ← 新增（建库建用户）
    minio-init.sh                  ← 新增（创建bucket）
```
### `docker-compose.middleware.yaml`
```yaml
services:
  postgres:
    image: postgres:16-alpine
    environment:
      POSTGRES_DB: deerflow
      POSTGRES_USER: deerflow
      POSTGRES_PASSWORD: $POSTGRES_PASSWORD
    volumes:
      - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql/data
      - ./middleware/init-postgres.sql:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/init.sql
    ports:
      - "5432:5432"
    restart: unless-stopped
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD-SHELL", "pg_isready -U deerflow"]
      interval: 10s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 5
  redis:
    image: redis:7-alpine
    command: redis-server --maxmemory 2gb --maxmemory-policy allkeys-lru
    volumes:
      - redis_data:/data
    ports:
      - "6379:6379"
    restart: unless-stopped
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "redis-cli", "ping"]
      interval: 10s
      timeout: 3s
      retries: 5
  minio:
    image: minio/minio
    command: server /data --console-address ":9001"
    environment:
      MINIO_ROOT_USER: minioadmin
      MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD: $MINIO_SECRET_KEY
    volumes:
      - minio_data:/data
    ports:
      - "9000:9000"
      - "9001:9001"
    restart: unless-stopped
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "curl", "-f", "http://localhost:9000/minio/health/live"]
      interval: 10s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 5
volumes:
  postgres_data:
  redis_data:
  minio_data:
```
### 节点 A/B `docker-compose.yaml` 新增环境变量
gateway 和 langgraph 服务增加：
```yaml
environment:
  - POSTGRES_DSN=postgresql://deerflow:${POSTGRES_PASSWORD}@node-c:5432/deerflow
  - REDIS_URL=redis://node-c:6379/0
  - MINIO_ENDPOINT=node-c:9000
  - MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=minioadmin
  - MINIO_SECRET_KEY=${MINIO_SECRET_KEY}
depends_on:
  postgres:
    condition: service_healthy
```
### 前置 Nginx LB `nginx/lb.conf`
```nginx
upstream deerflow_nodes {
    least_conn;
    server node-a:2026;
    server node-b:2026;
    keepalive 32;
}
server {
    listen 80;
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://deerflow_nodes;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_buffering off;      # SSE 必须关闭，否则事件流会被缓冲
        proxy_cache off;
        proxy_read_timeout 3600s;
        proxy_set_header Connection '';
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
```
### 启动顺序
```bash
# 1. 节点A/C：启动中间件
docker compose -f docker-compose.middleware.yaml up -d
# 2. 等待中间件健康（约30秒）
docker compose -f docker-compose.middleware.yaml ps
# 3. 节点A、节点B：各自启动应用
docker compose up -d
# 4. 节点A：启动前置LB
docker compose -f docker-compose.lb.yaml up -d
```
